ProPack (RNC) Validate Mode 1 (42.70/28820)

ProPack (RNC) Key Mode 1 (42.70/28820)
--------------------------------------
The  16  bit  key  can be entered in either decimal or hexadecimal. If you
want  to  enter  it  in  decimal,  just  write the number as the password.
Hexadecimal  you  have to write a "0x" or "$" sign in the beginning of the
number.  The  library will automatic convert to the 16 bit key and give it
to  the  decruncher routine. This is valid for the other key-crunched data
too.

